folder: North Moore Street & Greenwich Street, Manhattan, NY
original_title: Manhattan: North Moore Street - Greenwich Street
text:
64-68 North Moore Street, south side, between Greenwich and Hudson Streets.
About 1916.

folder: Greenwich Street & North Moore Street, Manhattan, NY
original_title: Manhattan: Greenwich Street - North Moore Street
text:
Greenwich Street, north from North Moore Street. Overhead is the Ninth Avenue Elevated. The street car tracks are to be removed by the W. P. A. The intersection in the midground is Beach Street.

June 2, 1937

W. P. A. photo
Five Boroughs Project
